"title": "8787: opposition, to God's person and work",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8787: opposition, to god's person and work",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The forces of evil are antagonistic towards God, his people and his work, and believers must oppose them.</p>\n<h2>Targets of opposition from evil forces</h2>\n<h3>The Lord himself</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:1-Ps2:3\">PSA 2:1–2:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:3\">HEB 12:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:10\">ISA 63:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:51\">ACT 7:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:14\">REV 17:14</a></p>\n<h3>God's people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:1-Acts8:3\">ACT 8:1–8:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:1-Num16:3\">NUM 16:1–16:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam16:5-2Sam16:8\">2SA 16:5–16:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:6\">EST 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:18\">JER 18:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:9-Acts26:11\">ACT 26:9–26:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:14-2Tim4:15\">2TI 4:14–4:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:7\">REV 13:7</a></p>\n<h3>God's work</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:2\">1TH 2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:4-Ezra4:5\">EZR 4:4–4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:7-Neh4:8\">NEH 4:7–4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:18\">ACT 4:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:8\">ACT 13:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:9\">1CO 16:9</a></p>\n<h2>Sources of opposition</h2>\n<h3>The world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:18-John15:19\">JHN 15:18–15:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:14\">JHN 17:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:13\">1JN 3:13</a></p>\n<h3>The flesh</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:17\">GAL 5:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:41\">MAT 26:41</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:38\">MRK 14:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:23\">ROM 7:23</a></p>\n<h3>The devil</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:8\">1PE 5:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech3:1\">ZEC 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:38-Matt13:39\">MAT 13:38–13:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">REV 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:4\">REV 12:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:7\">REV 12:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:9\">REV 12:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:13\">REV 12:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:17\">REV 12:17</a></p>\n<h2>Strategies used in opposition</h2>\n<h3>Shows of strength</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:5\">JDG 6:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:10-1Sam17:11\">1SA 17:10–17:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:14\">2KI 6:14</a></p>\n<h3>Discouraging propaganda</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:19-2Kgs18:22\">2KI 18:19–18:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:4-Rev13:6\">REV 13:4–13:6</a></p>\n<h3>Surprise</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:11-Gen39:12\">GEN 39:11–39:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:8-Ps10:9\">PSA 10:8–10:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps64:4\">PSA 64:4</a></p>\n<h3>Seduction</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:9\">MAT 4:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:15-1John2:16\">1JN 2:15–2:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:14\">REV 2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:20\">REV 2:20</a></p>\n<h3>Deceitfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:4\">JUD 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:16\">NUM 31:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:17\">1SA 18:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:1-Neh6:2\">NEH 6:1–6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:18\">ROM 16:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:13-2Cor11:15\">2CO 11:13–11:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:7\">2JN 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:8\">2JN 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:20\">REV 19:20</a></p>\n<h3>Sustained pressure</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:10\">GEN 39:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:6-1Sam1:7\">1SA 1:6–1:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:25\">2KI 6:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:4\">NEH 6:4</a></p>\n<h2>Motives for opposition</h2>\n<h3>Jealousy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:9\">1SA 18:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:16-Ps106:18\">PSA 106:16–106:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:18\">MAT 27:18</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:10\">MRK 15:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:17-Acts5:18\">ACT 5:17–5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:45\">ACT 13:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:5\">ACT 17:5</a></p>\n<h3>Troubled conscience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:7\">JHN 7:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:10\">ISA 30:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:14\">ACT 26:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:12\">1JN 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:10\">REV 11:10</a></p>\n<h3>Vested interests</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:19\">ACT 16:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:24-Acts19:27\">ACT 19:24–19:27</a></p>\n<h3>No just cause</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:4\">PSA 69:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:25\">JHN 15:25</a></p>\n<h2>Dealing with opposition</h2>\n<h3>Being prepared</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:17\">2PE 3:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:4\">2CO 10:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:9\">MRK 13:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:1-John16:4\">JHN 16:1–16:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:12\">1PE 4:12</a></p>\n<h3>Keeping a right perspective</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:15-2Kgs6:17\">2KI 6:15–6:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:14\">NEH 4:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:31\">ROM 8:31</a></p>\n<h3>Prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:9\">NEH 6:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:4\">NEH 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:7\">LUK 18:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:23-Acts4:24\">ACT 4:23–4:24</a></p>\n<h3>Patience</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:25\">2TI 2:25</a></p>\n<h3>Prudence</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:1-Judg8:3\">JDG 8:1–8:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:1\">PRO 15:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:25\">ACT 22:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:6\">ACT 23:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts25:11\">ACT 25:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:3\">2CO 6:3</a></p>\n<h3>Perseverance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:58\">1CO 15:58</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:27-Phil1:28\">PHP 1:27–1:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:9\">1PE 5:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:9\">REV 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:10\">REV 13:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:12\">REV 14:12</a></p>",
